sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Calendar Events Create Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open calendar events page
    UI->>LW: mount()
    LW->>DB: Query institute options
    DB-->>LW: Institutes list
    LW-->>UI: Render create event forms

    User->>UI: Select institute/campus/programme/module
    UI->>LW: updatedClass* handlers
    LW->>DB: Query dependent options (campus, class, module)
    DB-->>LW: Filtered options
    LW-->>UI: Re-render chained selects

    User->>UI: Save class/institute/public event
    UI->>LW: saveClassEvent() / saveInstituteHoliday() / savePublicHoliday()
    LW->>DB: Validate and insert calendar event row
    DB-->>LW: Event created
    LW-->>UI: Success toast + reset form
